Package: shinyglass
Type: Package
Title: Apple's Liquid Glass Design for Shiny Applications
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Eric", "Anderson", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "eric.ray.anderson@gmail.com")
Description: One function — glass_theme() — brings Apple's Liquid Glass aesthetic
    to Shiny apps. Built on bslib, it styles Bootstrap components with
    translucent surfaces, backdrop blur, and system typography.
